@NODE INTRODUCTION "Introduction"
@{fg shine}@{bg text} Introduction @{fg text}@{bg back}@{" Disclaimer " Link DISCLAIMER}@{" Install " Link INSTALLATION}@{" Config " Link CONFIG}@{" History " Link HISTORY}@{" Thanks " Link THANX}@{" Bugs? " Link BUGS}

         FullDED is a Xenolink BBS Full-Screen-Description Editor.


  Requirements:
  -------------

  o Xenolink BBS Professional
  o Amiga or compatibel computer.
  o Some filedesc's to write/edit :)

  What it is:
  -------------

    FullDed is the ultimate replace for Xenolink's Ded. It is used whenever
    you enter/edit a file description.

    It's a powerfull editor, with funktions like:

          o Zap and restart :)
            Well, just zap it and start over...

          o Add line
            Insert a new line and move the rest one step down.

          o Delete line
            Delete a line and move the rest one step up.

          o Zap line
            Remove the linetext.

          o Insertmode on/off
            Insert char or overwrite.

          o Freehand edit on/off
            Move only over text or free.

          o WordWrap on/off
            Wrap word at end of line.

          o Undo
            Reload as the start desciption (Only in edit or with DizFix)

          o Reload last description
            Open the last desc, great for multidisk files.

          o Center line
            Autocenter the line! No more counting.

          o Redraw
            If ANSI bug for the user, he can redraw and get it rigth.

          o FULL config
            You can config all texts, colors and placings.

@ENDNODE

