                             FullDed History.

  V2.0 10.Aug.96 -

ADD:

o ESC ESC for abort. Requested by Peter Sarstrom.
o Config file.
o Editable sceenlayout.
o Made the doc's to AmigaGuide.

  V1.1 03.Aug.96 -


First Aminet release.

ADD:

o CTRL-U for Undo, it will reload the original description again.

Bugfix:

o Delete in Insertmode maked some fun stuff :).
o Dizlines with 45 chars added an extra CR.


  V1.0 03.Aug.96 -

First public release.


